{"tid":1427960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【已FC】7仔保安部真係同狗合作！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:24:14.000Z","uid":245379,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f441edaca5f3bc341afb765010e60b7dcf86cbeb","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:25:38.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打開post話7仔保安部會交cctv片比狗<br />\n小弟身為7仔員工所以為大家確認個post既準確度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然而依家已經factcheck咗啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n以後去全港任何一間7仔買野 就算唔係手足都會比狗監視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變相根本同可能遲下會有既社交等級評分制一樣做每個舉動都被mon實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明便利店既cctv係防止有人偷野打劫但依家完全係違反私隱權！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TugvADY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTugvADY.jpg&h=3ef0f486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我鋪頭經理係個區既最大經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就聲稱話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無啲咁既事</span></strong></span><br />\n因為正常要拎cctv既片需要係我地員工去報警 狗先有權拎片<br />\n<br />\n咁我鋪經理就抱住小弟既疑問去問保安部主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>結果得到咁既回覆</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZP3JVJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZP3JVJH.jpg&h=fb9691fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗唔好浪費大家時間 重點圈埋你大家睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CR1Wwhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCR1Wwhm.jpg&h=67795e33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">此乃嚴重侵犯個人私隱！！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然小弟係7仔員工 但身在曹營心在漢<br />\n大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9615555239d3b89159a0bcae9c7682fce3a33871","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"自推10下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c4c804f4ac7d05719e0627acb802526dc275a2","tid":1427960,"uid":7482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣叫FC?"},{"pid":"c1ad53117403a02eb8ab66240829c704d8cde26d","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c4c804f4ac7d05719e0627acb802526dc275a2","tid":1427960,"uid":7482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣叫FC?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"網絡斷咗 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd52cdb5f01988a7ce4003afcaee3ad7aeba1baf","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:34:47.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b11f82eba25e6468761036d5a66d8d5127b3679c","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5c1d04d859ad365d9a8a0fee0cce22f4751e3bae","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9318bcb2aa3a674c24b39105e83d573e0dfe4918","tid":1427960,"uid":245379,"like":0,"dislike"